34&nbsp;W\u00b7h battery capacity (42&nbsp;mm)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ifixit.com/Store/Smartwatch/Apple-Watch-42-mm-Series-3-Cellular-Replacement-Battery/IF374-015?o=2|title=Apple Watch (42 mm Series 3 Cellular) Replacement Battery - iFixit|accessdate=8 October 2019|}}</ref>\n|'''40&nbsp;mm''': 224.9&nbsp;mA\u00b7h, 3.81&nbsp;V, 0.858&nbsp;W\u00b7h battery capacity<ref name=\"LloydS5-40mm\" /><br /> \n\n'''44&nbsp;mm''': 291.8&nbsp;mA\u00b7h, 3.81&nbsp;V, 1.113&nbsp;W\u00b7h battery capacity<ref name=\"IFixIt9-24-2018\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ifixit.com/Teardown/Apple+Watch+Series+4+Teardown/113044|title=Apple Watch Series 4 Teardown|date=September 24, 2018|website=[[IFixIt]]|access-date=September 29, 2019}}</ref>\n|'''40&nbsp;mm''': 245&nbsp;mA\u00b7h, 3.85&nbsp;V, 0.944&nbsp;W\u00b7h battery capacity<ref name=\"LloydS5-40mm\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ifixit.com/News/40mm-apple-watch-series-5-new-battery-design|title=The 40mm Apple Watch Series 5 Has a Radical New Battery Design|last=Lloyd|first=Craig|date=September 26, 2019|website=[[IFixIt]]|access-date=September 29, 2019}}</ref><br /> \n\n'''44&nbsp;mm''': 296&nbsp;mA\u00b7h, 3.814&nbsp;V, 1.129&nbsp;W\u00b7h battery capacity<ref name=\"LloydS5-44mm\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ifixit.com/News/apple-watch-series-5-teardown|title=Apple Watch Series 5 Teardown|last=Lloyd|first=Craig|date=September 25, 2019|website=[[IFixIt]]|access-date=September 29, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n!Weight\n|25g<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/kb/SP736?locale=en_US|title=Apple Watch Sport (1st generation) - Technical Specifications|website=support.apple.com|access-date=2019-09-19}}</ref> to 69g<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/kb/SP737?locale=en_US|title=Apple Watch Edition (1st generation) - Technical Specifications|website=support.apple.com|access-date=2019-09-19}}</ref>\n|25g to 30g <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/kb/SP745?locale=en_US|title=Apple Watch Series 1 - Technical Specifications|