=|archive-date=|access-date=September 12, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n!Introduced\n|April 2015\n|September 2016\n|September 2016\n|September 2017\n|September 2018\n|September 2019\n|-\n!Discontinued\n|September 2016\n|September 2018\n|September 2017\n|\n|September 2019\n|\n|-\n!Model Numbers<ref name=\"Identify\">{{cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204507|title=Identify your Apple Watch|date=September 19, 2019|website=[[support.apple.com]]|access-date=September 29, 2019}}</ref>\n|A1553 (38mm) A1554 (42mm)\n|A1802 (38mm) A1803 (42mm)\n|A1757 (38mm) A1758 (42mm)<br />'''Edition:''' A1816 (38mm) A1817 (42mm)\n|'''GPS:''' A1858 (38mm) A1859 (42mm)<br />'''GPS + Cellular:'''<br />Americas: A1860 (38mm) A1861 (42mm)<br />Europe and Asia Pacific: A1889 (38mm) A1891 (42mm)<br />China mainland: A1890 (38mm) A1892 (42mm)\n|'''GPS:''' A1977 (40mm) A1978 (44mm)<br />'''GPS + Cellular:'''<br />North America: A1975 (40mm) A1976 (44mm)<br />Europe, Asia Pacific, and China mainland: A2007 (40mm) A2008 (44mm)\n|'''GPS:''' A2092 (40mm), A2093 (44mm)<br />'''GPS + Cellular:'''<br />North America: A2094 (40mm) A2095 (44mm)<br />Europe, Asia Pacific, and China mainland: A2156 (40mm) A2157 (44mm)\n|-\n!FCC ID\n|BCG-E2870<ref>{{cite web|url=https://electric.garden/BCG-E2870?fccid|title=E2870 Apple Watch A1153 38mm (First Generation) by Apple|accessdate=8 October 2019}}</ref> BCG-E2871<ref>{{cite web|url=https://electric.garden/BCG-E2871?fccid|title=E2871 Apple Watch A1154 42mm (First Generation) by Apple|accessdate=8 October 2019}}</ref>\n|BCG-E3102<ref>{{cite web|url=https://electric.garden/BCG-E3102?fccid|title=E3102 Apple Watch Series 1 A1802 38mm by Apple|accessdate=8 October 2019}}</ref> BCG-E3103<ref>{{cite web|url=https://electric.garden/BCG-E3103?fccid|title=E3103 Apple Watch Series 1 A1803 42mm by Apple|accessdate=8 October 2019}}</ref>\n|BCG-E3104<ref>{{cite web|url=https://electric.garden/BCG-E3104?fccid|title=E3104 Apple Watch Series 2 A1757 & A1816 38mm by Apple|accessdate